room_title: Escape room "The Witching Hour" by Locked Manhattan in Manhattan
room_description: The town mayor reached out to you to assist in an investigation of a mysterious woman living on the outskirts of town. Her strange behavior has risen suspicion amongst the townsfolk, especially during a time like this, when the town seems to be cursed. Search through the woman's apartment, look for her spell book and escape her house. For, unbeknownst to you, she has been waiting for this night perhaps with more anticipation than you have...
